wikipedia_page.main: Nicholas Cadden (born 19 September 1996) is a Scottish professional footballer who plays as a winger for Forest Green Rovers. Cadden has previously played for Airdrieonians, Livingston, Ayr United and Greenock Morton. He is the twin brother of Chris Cadden.
